  "original_title": "13 \u0b86\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "13th Amendment Act should be implemented in full: Minister Douglas's message to President Ranil",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Douglas Devananda has informed the acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe that if there is an opportunity to lead the country, taking into consideration the political aspirations of the Tamil people, steps should be taken to fully implement the 13th Amendment Act of the Constitution.",
        "The matter was emphasized during today's discussion between the Prime Minister and Minister Douglas Devananda regarding the current conditions of the country and the measures to be taken to rescue the country from the economic crisis.",
        "Accepting the opinion of the Minister, the Prime Minister said that his expectation is to create a prosperous future for the country by promoting things on the basis of the Constitution.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Eelam People's Democratic Party has continuously emphasized that moving forward with the full implementation of the 13th Amendment Act is a practical and feasible way to achieve the political aspirations of the Tamil people."
      ],
